<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">被减数连减n个数，可以先减去与被减数末几位相同的减数，然后再减去其他数，即得其结果。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">1267-636-167=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">1267-636-167</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1267-167-636</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1100-636</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=464</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>